|GKO================================================================
                             |CKOLeap
|GKO================================================================

|YKOLeap allows a Garou to jump onto a surprised opponent
and get a free attack. It must either be used from an
adjacent room, or by a blended wolf. Success is not
guaranteed.

|WKOSyntax: |YKBleap at <target> |WKOor |YKBleap <dir> at <target>
|WKOCost: |CKO25 sps
